headline: NCLH's Debt Refinancing Momentum Builds: Is Balance Sheet Risk Easing?
summary: Norwegian Cruise refinances about $2B of debt, removes secured notes, extends maturities and cuts share count, all while keeping leverage essentially flat.

headline: Q3 Earnings Roundup: Royal Caribbean (NYSE:RCL) And The Rest Of The Travel and Vacation Providers Segment
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Royal Caribbean (NYSE:RCL) and the rest of the travel and vacation providers stocks fared in Q3.
